abstract: Former Cleveland Browns quarterback Johnny Manziel is booked and posts bond in misdemeanor domestic violence case in Dallas; other pro football news noted.
lead_paragraph: Manziel, a 23-year-old former quarterback for the Cleveland Browns, was booked and posted bond in a domestic violence case in Dallas on Wednesday.
